dmca.title: Ordo Templi Orientis Complains of Copyright Infringement
dmca.body:
FAX MEMORANDUM 
April 14, 2005

Ordo Templi Orientis (O.T.O.)
(a California not-for-profit corporation) 
[Private]
New York NY 10116 USA
[Private]@mac.com

Google Inc.
Attn: User Support, DMCA complaints
[Private]
Mountain View, CA 94043
[Private], Attn: User Support, DMCA complaints

Dear Sir or Madam

This is a complaint under the US DMCA as well as the Canadian Copyright Act.

The copyrighted work at issue is the text that appears at

http://groups.google.ca/
groups?hl=en&lr=&selm=q6es60tl45bb9n1q90ak6b3o7v6snrq9r4%404ax.com

The infringed work is "Emblems and Modes of Use," and the author is Aleister Crowley. Mes
